Llan kra n yemdanen ur numin ara s Ɛisa Lmasiḥ, tessers-aɣ-d acḥal i yelha m'ara nqehheṛ wid ur numin ara s Lmasiḥ,
Deg ussan-nni, a d-yas lweqt i deg ara ɛeddin lɛid n Tfaska, bɣan ad kksen di leqsed n lɛid n izimer n leslak. Ma d kečč tzemreḍ aț-țestenfeɛt, aț-țiliḍ di tafat n tafat n yiṭij.
Ilaq a k-n-iniɣ belli aț-țiliḍ d sebba n zzux i gellan di tejmaɛt n imasiḥiyen : ilit d uselmed n tideț, a d-tban acḥal meqqṛet tezmert n tejmaɛt n imasiḥiyen akken ilaq.
Di tejmaɛt n temdint n Lquds, llan kra wussan n temdarin di mkul lɛid n Tfaska, setɛeṛfen belli d ayen yeɛnan lɛid n leslak i deg ilaq ad nehhun Lmasiḥ, mkul ass n lɛid n wass wis xemsin.
Ayen akk i d-ițwaxelqen deg yiwet n tɣuṛfeț, ger idurar, deg ifran d mkul amkan, mkul amkan n tmurt ama ț-țaɛewdiw neɣ djaj yețṛeqṛiqen.
Imi nuggad a ɣ-yawi waḍu ɣer leryuf iweɛṛen n tmurt n Libya, ncudd lbabuṛ s imurar ; nerna nṣubb-ed lbac-nni s wayes i t-yețțawi waḍu, neǧǧa iman-nneɣ a ɣ-yawi ɣer wanda yebɣa.
M'ara d-yaweḍ wass i deg ara nsel i tmurt n Galasya : i gellan di mkul amkan yesseǧsen aṭas n iqelwacen akk-d wid yeznuzun, i iɛewdiwen d wid i ten-irekben, i t-irekben ad uɣalen ɣer weqṛaḥ n wuzzal akk-d wukrif nniḍen.
M'ara n-yali yiṭij s leḥmu-ines yesseṛɣayen, imɣi ad iqqaṛ, ajeǧǧig-is ad iɣli, ccbaḥa-ines a s-tṛuḥ.
Dexxan n tmes s wayes ara nɛețțaben ad yeqqim si lǧil ɣer lǧil ; wid yețseǧǧiden zdat leɛqiṛa d lmeṣuɛ ines akk-d kra win iqeblen ticṛeṭ n igenni, ur steɛfayen ara iḍ d wass.
Eɛni aț-țɛiceḍ di tafat yeɛnan igenni ? Tajmaɛt-agi, ț-țikli deg igenwan, axaṭer ț-țikli-k di tecbuct-agi i d-yețțaken tafat.
Xedmeɣ yerna nneɛtabeɣ aṭas, acḥal d abrid țțuẓumeɣ, zgiɣ deg uɛawez, iwakken aț-ț terbaɛtem atmaten n tmurt-nneɣ.
Yella wayen i d-ibeggnen annect agi, axaṭer yeffeɣ-ed abeṛnus-nni i ččiɣ, a d-uɣalen ɣer webrid s yisem n Sidi Ṛebbi.
Ilemẓi-agi d ayen yețwaxedmen s ufus n wemdan, imi d ɣuṛ-es i gella lḥal yellan deg umkan-is. Yura di tira iqedsen : Mačči d wid iteddun i gzemren ad ifhem wid yețɛeddayen syenna.
Argaz-agi ixeddem akka imi d ameksa kan yețwaxelṣen, ur as tewqiɛ ara deg lewḥuc iweɛṛen, lameɛna ad țțaɣen awal i lecyux-nsen.
